{"tid":1840480,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一圖概括袁國勇論文三大重點","createTime":"2020-01-25T00:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T23:42:20.000Z","uid":38861,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b082338dfda16c24226b6a4420c5a91fff233c","tid":1840480,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:07:17.000Z","msg":"A familial cluster of pneumonia associated with the 2019 novel coronavirus indicating person-to-person transmission: a study of a family cluster<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flancet%2Farticle%2FPIIS0140-6736%2820&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=0bd48f3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20</a>)30154-9/fulltext<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JersqoS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJersqoS.jpg&h=3ba58f90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.首學術文章證實武漢肺炎病毒能以<strong>人傳人</strong>的方式傳播。<br />\n<br />\n2.武漢肺炎病毒與SARS病毒的某一個受體區域(external subdomain region of receptor binding domain of Spike subunit 1)的蛋白質排組並不相似，<br />\n推斷兩者在人體內引起的反應<strong>可能</strong>會有所不同。<br />\n<br />\n3.武漢肺炎病毒<strong>並無統一徵狀可概括</strong>。"},{"pid":"345c5598ed747fcc5e7f40973b80ba3e351550fc","tid":1840480,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:14:37.000Z","msg":"清楚明白"},{"pid":"ce2f388370659976c0a92205a0ddcc6c5e4a923d","tid":1840480,"uid":289751,"like":9,"dislike":12,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:17:18.000Z","msg":"如果你做教書上你堂應該好開心<br />\nBtw可以拎你既圖做头宣"},{"pid":"a50cf50ae3c918076b0af80e9ab75a3d2d5e9c78","tid":1840480,"uid":38861,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ce2f388370659976c0a92205a0ddcc6c5e4a923d","tid":1840480,"uid":289751,"like":9,"dislike":12,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:17:18.0